name: Burger with a side of 747? Plane Spotting LAX 2020
description:
When you think about seeing the action at LAX, there's only one planespotting location that comes to mind: The In-N-Out Burger at 9149 S Sepulveda Blvd, Los Angeles, CA 90045. In this video, I'll share some of the planes I spotted while I was there one Saturday morning in January. 

It was a fun few hours and culminated in a killer cheeseburger from the In-N-Out Burger LAX.
